name: DIRTY PRESETS: VINTAGE FILM - VOLUME III
description:
Professional photographer Dustin Hollywood has spent the last 3 years developing a style so unique that you can recognize his work merely by its tones and lighting techniques.  Over the years he has developed over 100 individual and unique presets and filters to produce his amazing photos.  These presets are just that, presets that can be applied to your photo, whether shot in natural light or flash, to reach a certain look and feel his vintage work is known for.  Ranging the entire color tone spectrum including B&W.  This is the third volume of presets to be released by the photographer this year, with more coming in the future.

The DIRTY PRESETS: VINTAGE FILM - VOLUME III:  includes 16 fresh vintage grain B&W presets of your favorite film from Kodak / Ilford / Holga specifically for Adobe Lightroom 4 & 5, designed by professional fashion/music photographer Dustin Hollywood.  These Presets will give your photographs that vintage film feel on your otherwise modern digital photographs and take your work creatively farther.

This pack is cool tones only.

name: EDM VOLUME I : A PHOTOGRAPH COLLECTION 2009-2013
description:
The first photo/coffee table book from professional photographer and designer Dustin Hollywood.  The book is one of the first of its kind, showcasing the current rise and popularity of the Electronic Dance Music, or EDM, musical craze right now.  Focusing on his travels and experiences from 2009 - 2013, this book covers some of the biggest names in the business such as Steve Aoki, Skrillex, Avicii, Tiesto, Justin Martin, LA Riots, Justice, LMFAO, Bro Safari, Flux Pavilion, The Twelves, Datsik, Felix Cartal, Clockwork, Dirtyphonics, Le Castle Vania, Miami Horror, and many many more!  

Dustin combines his vintage love with modern twists.  Combining grunge aesthetics with mirroring, light techniques, and multiple exposures he creates works that are far from the norm in live music photography.
